title: Are Elon Musk and Sam Altman not ‘human’? Internet erupts after podcaster’s claim goes viral as Donald Trump teases UFO files
description: A social media post by conservative commentator Candace Owens has resurfaced after former US president Donald Trump said he would direct federal agencies to begin identifying and releasing government files related to aliens and unidentified flying objects. The older clip, in which Owens suggested that technology figures including Elon Musk, Peter Thiel and Sam Altman were “not human”, has circulated widely across X in recent days. The renewed attention follows Trump’s statement on Truth Social that his administration would move to release material concerning extraterrestrial life, unidentified aerial phenomena and UFOs, citing strong public interest.
